### 備品一覧
GET http://localhost:8080/api/equipments

### 備品登録
POST http://localhost:8080/api/equipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "USB-C ドッキングステーション",
  "category": "周辺機器"
}

### 備品貸出
POST http://localhost:8080/api/equipments/1/lend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "山田太郎"
}

### 備品返却
POST http://localhost:8080/api/equipments/1/return

### 貸出履歴一覧
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rental-records
